701170f.title: Bronx: Grand Concourse - Echo Place
701170f.text:
Grand Concourse, north from Echo Place. W.P.A. men are seen working
on the repavement of the east lane of the thoroughfare.
March 31, 1936.
Works Progress Administration.
Federal Art Project photo.
